item.title: Love Is Your Choice
item.description:
In this thought-provoking episode, Elaine shares a personal experience that taught her a profound lesson about the power of assigning meaning and choosing love in our daily lives.

Through her captivating storytelling, Elaine takes listeners on a journey of self-reflection and awareness. She explores the concept of noticing the love that is present in every situation and reminds us that we have the power to choose the love we experience...
